{"tid":2455723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"料結合健康碼作疫苗護照","createTime":"2021-03-21T10:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T10:59:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9fdf7e1172acf132e979509ad33c511fe1b91017","tid":2455723,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210321/LWECUYJMT5EWLPIF6LRD74RTB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210321%2FLWECUYJMT5EWLPIF6LRD74RTB4%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=ac2e7bc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210321%2FLWECUYJMT5EWLPIF6LRD74RTB4%2F&h=332d2046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210321/LWECUYJMT5EWLPIF6LRD74RTB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n料結合健康碼作疫苗護照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3MysX7zA2urUnfZYMFjK_oN2LxY=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AO7ID6HY5FCPFOPKJJD53A3YOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3MysX7zA2urUnfZYMFjK_oN2LxY%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAO7ID6HY5FCPFOPKJJD53A3YOU.jpg&h=af106ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■智方便上月新增電子針卡功能。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】世界各國陸續展開接種疫苗計劃，多國包括歐盟等正商討建立「疫苗護照」計劃，讓接種疫苗後的國民恢復出境旅遊活動。創科局局長薛永恒月初表示，曾考慮推行疫苗護照，並以電子針卡配合實行針卡互通，惟現時仍須視乎疫情發展決定。有專家預料，政府或以「智方便」應用程式結合健康碼等系統作出入境證明，變相強制市民下載。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憂強制出境市民下載<br />\n<br />\n現時不少國家已設立疫苗護照計劃，其中內地早前推出「國際旅行健康證明」，未來可用以出行旅遊，以提升疫苗接種率。根據本港疫苗接種計劃網頁顯示，電子針卡系統是讓市民下載疫苗接種紀錄，並在有需要時展示，例如進行強制檢測時供政府部門查核，但聲稱市民不一定要申請電子針卡，相關紀錄現時亦暫不會用作出入境用途。<br />\n<br />\n不過，旅遊界立法會議員姚思榮日前表示，本港現時有條件探討疫苗護照，商經局局長邱騰華亦透露，港府正研究相關安排，或考慮以電子針卡作出入境免檢疫安排。香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑認為，政府或將智方便與健康碼等認證系統結合，市民須持有電子針卡才可獲取入境認證，「你一張爛紙太易偽造喇，一定係會透過電子渠道去做」。<br />\n<br />\n民主派資訊科技界選委黃浩華質疑，智方便涉及私隱問題，通關後更有可能將用戶資料轉移給第三方，擔心政府強制出境的市民下載。他相信政策推出將遇上極大阻力，「我個人而言會對呢個做法有質疑囉」。"},{"pid":"8c9b8ebbff2cedcf2e22f74a25e0fcc9ef54bea2","tid":2455723,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"打科興冇人同你互認囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9dd9c9359e8fcbc69f87ff10ae8da6f4dc8936","tid":2455723,"uid":325586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"打科興邊d 發達國家會認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb625856890333aac2d8f515ab3ff01d00b4514e","tid":2455723,"uid":137038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:48:59.000Z","msg":"DSE證書同大學畢業證書又唔話係爛紙一張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a0934bc8002df3601c039e7f7eea9f81e05819","tid":2455723,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"已經習慣唔洗去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e740e09d78d0f065e5423e322c33b827a55a74dd","tid":2455723,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a9dd9c9359e8fcbc69f87ff10ae8da6f4dc8936","tid":2455723,"uid":325586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"打科興邊d 發達國家會認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"非洲兄弟蟈家<br />\n<br />\n唔知契哥玩唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088aa7e19116ac037fe3a478d69d3cc1bdeacd3d","tid":2455723,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"咁肯定出現第五次疫症高峰期"},{"pid":"d57c772623473b2a42e2c506246aca9db04f6f96","tid":2455723,"uid":260744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"乜證書都係一張爛紙嚟嫁啦"},{"pid":"c1ea715ae2c28b6b4c459b024da303f5f300a76e","tid":2455723,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"冇西方國家應你d支苗喎，日本都未必去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}